metadata.name: SUNFLOWER DATA FARM
metadata.description:
The first in the Wandering Sleep collection and my genesis project on Foundation. 

After my recent adventure as a virtually broke sunflower, absorbing free data and arguing with tech moguls and naturalists, I was inspired to write this song 'Ya Ya' and create my second animation visual. 

Buy my NFT to support the development of my metaverse fiction malfnktion.inspace ┏(＾0＾)┛
